README.md
     1Ôćĺ# humanize
    12ÔćĺThis modest package contains various common humanization utilities, like turning a
    13Ôćĺnumber into a fuzzy human-readable duration ("3 minutes ago") or into a human-readable
    14Ôćĺsize or throughput. It is localized to:
    15Ôćĺ
    16Ôćĺ- Arabic
    17Ôćĺ- Basque
    18Ôćĺ- Bengali
    19Ôćĺ- Brazilian Portuguese
    20Ôćĺ- Catalan
    21Ôćĺ- Danish
    22Ôćĺ- Dutch
    23Ôćĺ- Esperanto
    24Ôćĺ- European Portuguese
    25Ôćĺ- Finnish
    26Ôćĺ- French
    27Ôćĺ- German
    28Ôćĺ- Greek
    29Ôćĺ- Hebrew
    30Ôćĺ- Indonesian
    31Ôćĺ- Italian
    32Ôćĺ- Japanese
    33Ôćĺ- Klingon
    34Ôćĺ- Korean
    35Ôćĺ- Norwegian
    36Ôćĺ- Persian
    37Ôćĺ- Polish
    38Ôćĺ- Russian
    39Ôćĺ- Simplified Chinese
    40Ôćĺ- Slovak
    41Ôćĺ- Slovenian
    42Ôćĺ- Spanish
    43Ôćĺ- Swedish
    44Ôćĺ- Turkish
    45Ôćĺ- Ukrainian
    46Ôćĺ- Uzbek
    47Ôćĺ- Vietnamese
