    49Ôćĺ## API reference
    51Ôćĺ[https://humanize.readthedocs.io](https://humanize.readthedocs.io/)
    52Ôćĺ
    53Ôćĺ<!-- usage-start -->
    54Ôćĺ
    55Ôćĺ## Installation
    57Ôćĺ### From PyPI
    59Ôćĺ```bash
    60Ôćĺpython3 -m pip install --upgrade humanize
    61Ôćĺ```
    62Ôćĺ
    63Ôćĺ### From source
    65Ôćĺ```bash
    66Ôćĺgit clone https://github.com/python-humanize/humanize
    67Ôćĺcd humanize
    68Ôćĺpython3 -m pip install -e .
    69Ôćĺ```
    70Ôćĺ
    71Ôćĺ## Usage
    73Ôćĺ### Integer humanization
    75Ôćĺ```pycon
    76Ôćĺ>>> import humanize
    77Ôćĺ>>> humanize.intcomma(12345)
    78Ôćĺ'12,345'
    79Ôćĺ>>> humanize.intword(123455913)
    80Ôćĺ'123.5 million'
    81Ôćĺ>>> humanize.intword(12345591313)
    82Ôćĺ'12.3 billion'
    83Ôćĺ>>> humanize.apnumber(4)
    84Ôćĺ'four'
    85Ôćĺ>>> humanize.apnumber(41)
    86Ôćĺ'41'
    87Ôćĺ```
    88Ôćĺ
    89Ôćĺ### Date & time humanization
    91Ôćĺ```pycon
    92Ôćĺ>>> import humanize
    93Ôćĺ>>> import datetime as dt
    94Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturalday(dt.datetime.now())
    95Ôćĺ'today'
    96Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturaldelta(dt.timedelta(seconds=1001))
    97Ôćĺ'16 minutes'
    98Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturalday(dt.datetime.now() - dt.timedelta(days=1))
    99Ôćĺ'yesterday'
   100Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturalday(dt.date(2007, 6, 5))
   101Ôćĺ'Jun 05'
   102Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturaldate(dt.date(2007, 6, 5))
   103Ôćĺ'Jun 05 2007'
   104Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.datetime.now() - dt.timedelta(seconds=1))
   105Ôćĺ'a second ago'
   106Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.datetime.now() - dt.timedelta(seconds=3600))
   107Ôćĺ'an hour ago'
   108Ôćĺ```
   109Ôćĺ
   110Ôćĺ### Precise time delta
   112Ôćĺ```pycon
   113Ôćĺ>>> import humanize
   114Ôćĺ>>> import datetime as dt
   115Ôćĺ>>> delta = dt.timedelta(seconds=3633, days=2, microseconds=123000)
   116Ôćĺ>>> humanize.precisedelta(delta)
   117Ôćĺ'2 days, 1 hour and 33.12 seconds'
   118Ôćĺ>>> humanize.precisedelta(delta, minimum_unit="microseconds")
   119Ôćĺ'2 days, 1 hour, 33 seconds and 123 milliseconds'
   120Ôćĺ>>> humanize.precisedelta(delta, suppress=["days"], format="%0.4f")
   121Ôćĺ'49 hours and 33.1230 seconds'
   122Ôćĺ```
   123Ôćĺ
   124Ôćĺ#### Smaller units
   126ÔćĺIf seconds are too large, set `minimum_unit` to milliseconds or microseconds:
   127Ôćĺ
   128Ôćĺ```pycon
   129Ôćĺ>>> import humanize
   130Ôćĺ>>> import datetime as dt
   131Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturaldelta(dt.timedelta(seconds=2))
   132Ôćĺ'2 seconds'
   133Ôćĺ```
   134Ôćĺ
   135Ôćĺ```pycon
   136Ôćĺ>>> delta = dt.timedelta(milliseconds=4)
   137Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturaldelta(delta)
   138Ôćĺ'a moment'
   139Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturaldelta(delta, minimum_unit="milliseconds")
   140Ôćĺ'4 milliseconds'
   141Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturaldelta(delta, minimum_unit="microseconds")
   142Ôćĺ'4 milliseconds'
   143Ôćĺ```
   144Ôćĺ
   145Ôćĺ```pycon
   146Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturaltime(delta)
   147Ôćĺ'now'
   148Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturaltime(delta, minimum_unit="milliseconds")
   149Ôćĺ'4 milliseconds ago'
   150Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturaltime(delta, minimum_unit="microseconds")
   151Ôćĺ'4 milliseconds ago'
   152Ôćĺ```
   153Ôćĺ
   154Ôćĺ### File size humanization
   156Ôćĺ```pycon
   157Ôćĺ>>> import humanize
   158Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturalsize(1_000_000)
   159Ôćĺ'1.0 MB'
   160Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturalsize(1_000_000, binary=True)
   161Ôćĺ'976.6 KiB'
   162Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturalsize(1_000_000, gnu=True)
   163Ôćĺ'976.6K'
   164Ôćĺ```
   165Ôćĺ
   166Ôćĺ### Human-readable floating point numbers
   168Ôćĺ```pycon
   169Ôćĺ>>> import humanize
   170Ôćĺ>>> humanize.fractional(1/3)
   171Ôćĺ'1/3'
   172Ôćĺ>>> humanize.fractional(1.5)
   173Ôćĺ'1 1/2'
   174Ôćĺ>>> humanize.fractional(0.3)
   175Ôćĺ'3/10'
   176Ôćĺ>>> humanize.fractional(0.333)
   177Ôćĺ'333/1000'
   178Ôćĺ>>> humanize.fractional(1)
   179Ôćĺ'1'
   180Ôćĺ```
   181Ôćĺ
   182Ôćĺ### Scientific notation
   184Ôćĺ```pycon
   185Ôćĺ>>> import humanize
   186Ôćĺ>>> humanize.scientific(0.3)
   187Ôćĺ'3.00 x 10Ôü╗┬╣'
   188Ôćĺ>>> humanize.scientific(500)
   189Ôćĺ'5.00 x 10┬▓'
   190Ôćĺ>>> humanize.scientific("20000")
   191Ôćĺ'2.00 x 10Ôü┤'
   192Ôćĺ>>> humanize.scientific(1**10)
   193Ôćĺ'1.00 x 10Ôü░'
   194Ôćĺ>>> humanize.scientific(1**10, precision=1)
   195Ôćĺ'1.0 x 10Ôü░'
   196Ôćĺ>>> humanize.scientific(1**10, precision=0)
   197Ôćĺ'1 x 10Ôü░'
   198Ôćĺ```
   199Ôćĺ
   200Ôćĺ## Localization
   202ÔćĺHow to change locale at runtime:
   203Ôćĺ
   204Ôćĺ```pycon
   205Ôćĺ>>> import humanize
   206Ôćĺ>>> import datetime as dt
   207Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.timedelta(seconds=3))
   208Ôćĺ'3 seconds ago'
   209Ôćĺ>>> _t = humanize.i18n.activate("ru_RU")
   210Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.timedelta(seconds=3))
   211Ôćĺ'3 ĐüđÁđ║ĐâđŻđ┤Đő đŻđ░đĚđ░đ┤'
   212Ôćĺ>>> humanize.i18n.deactivate()
   213Ôćĺ>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.timedelta(seconds=3))
   214Ôćĺ'3 seconds ago'
   215Ôćĺ```
   216Ôćĺ
   217ÔćĺYou can pass additional parameter `path` to `activate` to specify a path to search
   218Ôćĺlocales in.
   219Ôćĺ
   220Ôćĺ```pycon
   221Ôćĺ>>> import humanize
   222Ôćĺ>>> humanize.i18n.activate("xx_XX")
   223Ôćĺ<...>
   224ÔćĺFileNotFoundError: [Errno 2] No translation file found for domain: 'humanize'
   225Ôćĺ>>> humanize.i18n.activate("pt_BR", path="path/to/my/own/translation/")
   226Ôćĺ<gettext.GNUTranslations instance ...>
   227Ôćĺ```
   228Ôćĺ
   229Ôćĺ<!-- usage-end -->
   230Ôćĺ
   231ÔćĺHow to add new phrases to existing locale files:
   232Ôćĺ
   233Ôćĺ```sh
   234Ôćĺxgettext --from-code=UTF-8 -o humanize.pot -k'_' -k'N_' -k'P_:1c,2' -k'NS_:1,2' -k'_ngettext:1,2' -l python src/humanize/*.py  # extract new phrases
   235Ôćĺmsgmerge -U src/humanize/locale/ru_RU/LC_MESSAGES/humanize.po humanize.pot # add them to locale files
   236Ôćĺ```
   237Ôćĺ
